## Change 2: Adopt AI more

- **Planning and coding** — use AI agents for technical planning and writing code from tasks
- **I still own quality** — manually test implemented features before merging
- Agents handle boilerplate and implementation; I focus on design, review, and validation

## Change 1 + Change 2: Bonus

- More "free" time
- Generate code very fast -> very fast mvp
- Make a few small tools past 2 weeks

